WEBVTT

38:15.870 --> 38:17.600 line:80%
What is the matter, Grand Tutor?

38:17.600 --> 38:18.600 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,

38:18.600 --> 38:20.200 line:80%
in the Battle of Jinzhou years ago,

38:20.200 --> 38:21.720 line:80%
General Xie died in battle.

38:21.720 --> 38:22.830 line:80%
More than a decade later,

38:22.830 --> 38:25.560 line:80%
the fate of the Marquis of Wu'an
is still unknown.

38:25.800 --> 38:29.200 line:80%
Yet you still sent your only heir
